<a name="faq_spoiler_rule"></a>

<table class="tborder" cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" align="center">
<tr>
	<td class="tcat">Spoiler information</td>
</tr>

<tr>
	<td class="alt1"><div align="left"><font size="1">The Safehouse often discusses movies, television programs, games, and numerous other &quot;current event&quot; topics. Please keep in mind that when discussing the plot of a Movie, Book, Video Game or TV show, others may have not yet had the chance to see or play the topic in question. If you will be discussing anything related to plot twists or other spoiler type information, remember to enclose your spoiler comments in spoiler tags. samples: [spoiler] <i>comments go here</i>[/spoiler] </font>
<font size="1">Although it seems like a trivial matter, many people take this matter seriously. If you fail to follow these guidelines, you may find yourself with a week ban. </font></div></td>
</tr>


</table>

